game.name: Ariel And Elsa Career Dress Up
game.description:
Wow! Your favorite two Disney princesses Anna and Elsa have recently got their graduation degrees and planned out to go on their work. But, a problem arises in front of these two cuties when they are seeking for a job profile. What kind of profession among chef, waitress, painter or a singer they should choose? Luckily, they have a good friend like you who can help make a firm career dress decision. Join Ariel and Elsa Career Dress Up game and help them both to choose the suitable career options!
You do not need to bother at all since the right side of the screen will show you a huge collection of dress and makeup option to choose. Try them all one by one to decide which professional suit their personalities the most! Start with dressing up the first girl and then go with the second girl! Create any look among chef, waitress, painter and singer look for the first girl in this html5 dressing game for girls! Give her a nice top and combine it with a matching top along with a pair of suitable sandals or shoes! 
Make sure that her hand carries a tool which career option you want to give your girl. Click the next button to explore all the beauty products in this princess makeover game! Choose a nice hairstyle and combine her look with beautiful eye contact lenses, eye shadow, eye brows, and lipstick! Hurry up friends! Your second girl is also waiting for her turn. Follow the same instructions to dress her up with her desired career outfits! Good luck to impress both girls with your intelligence by dressing them up for their desired career style!
